original: Landqvist, Carl Valfrid, fastighetsdirektör, Norrköping, f. 29/9/89 i Hemmesjö, Kronob. 1. G. 15 m. Ruth Löf-qvist. Barn: Elsbeth f. 16, Kerstin 23. — Tj :man v. Ary bruk i Aryd 06-15, ’kont xhef v. Forssjö bruk i Katrineholm 15-27, fastighidir. i Norrköp. sed. 27. Ordf. i Norrköp. Träimp. A-B sed. 32, verkst. dir. i A-B Bostäder i Norrköp. sed. 37. Led. av Katrineholms stadsfullm. o. folksk istyr. t. 27, ordf. i tax:nd i Norrköp. t. 41. RVO.
translated: Landqvist, Carl Valfrid, Real Estate Director, Norrköping, b. 29/9/89 in Hemmesjö, Kronob. 1st marriage 15, with Ruth Löf-qvist. Children: Elsbeth b. 16, Kerstin b. 23. - Employed as a man at Ary bruk in Aryd from 1906-1915, assistant manager at Forssjö bruk in Katrineholm from 1915-1927, real estate director in Norrköping since 1927. Chairman of Norrköping Wood Imp. A-B since 1932, managing director of A-B Housing in Norrköping since 1937. Member of Katrineholm City Council and School Board until 1927, chairman of tax committee in Norrköping until 1941. RVO (Order of the Vasa).
